key_finding: Gradient methods find improvements but ALL cause overlaps. The current solution is at the boundary of the feasible region - any movement that reduces bounding box causes tree overlaps.
notes: Tested on N=2-30 with multiple optimizers. L-BFGS-B found improvements of 0.00001-0.14 but all had overlaps. Barrier method with mu=1e4-1e7 found no valid improvements. Differential evolution also failed to find valid improvements.
